German do-it-yourself home
improvement chain Bauhaus AG will invest 25 million euros
($34.97 million) in its first outlet in  Serbia , Beta newswire
reported, citing Bauhausâ€™ international affairs manager Helmut
Diewald.  The store in Belgrade will have more than 20,000 square
